Name: FTEN Cut Blocks Current and Application
NOW Centre Points with 500 metre radius
Old Growth Management Areas Non Legal
Scenic Areas in KSRMP
sqlquery: STRGC_LAND_RSRCE_PLAN_NAME = 'Kispiox Sustainable Resource Management Plan' AND LEGAL_FEAT_OBJECTIVE = 'Scenic Areas'

Name: Botanical Pine Mushrooms

Name: West Babine Berry Gathering

Name: SMZ
sqlquery: STRGC_LAND_RSRCE_PLAN_NAME = 'West Babine Sustainable Resource Management Plan' AND LEGAL_FEAT_OBJECTIVE = 'Special Management Zones'

Name: Kispiox RMZ
sqlquery: STRGC_LAND_RSRCE_PLAN_NAME LIKE 'Kisp%' AND LEGAL_FEAT_OBJECTIVE = 'Resource Management Zones' AND LEGAL_FEAT_ATRB_1_VALUE <> 'Kispiox'
